iOS 16
Our consistent iOS icon pack covers diverse theme categories and follows the guidelines from Apple. These icons are pixel-perfect at 50×50 pixels and the style is outline with the base stroke being 2px. All the icons have iOS Filled version. This pack works for iOS applications with vertical lists like iOS Mail App.
This is by far our most popular icon pack. The Icons8 team created all the icons in-house, started immediately after the iOS 7 release and drawing it up to this day.
Download free iOS icons on various themes for user interface design. The graphics are available in both png and vector. Also, don’t miss a pack of iOS Glyph icons and Animated iOS icons.
As well, welcome to check new icons and popular icons in 30+ design styles.
